40
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:33,000
- jadi saya... - Yiyi, awak

41
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,800
tergesa-gesa untuk membunuhnya,

42
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:37,590
ia benar-benar mengelirukan.

43
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,360
Hanyu,

44
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:40,840
awak pun tak percaya saya.

45
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:44,710
Mak Cik,

46
